Please see http://PyroRobotics.com/ for tutorials and detailed
documentation on installation, development, use, licensing, etc.


Prerequisites
=============

  * NumPy 1.8.x

Using Pyrobot
=============

Windows:

  > python bin/pyrobot.py

Linux:

  > make
  > pyrobot


Building Pyrobot
================

Fedora 10
---------

You'll need at least:

  yum install gcc gcc-c++ python python-devel swig libjpeg-devel ncurses-libs

You'll also need to fix a missing library link:

  ln -s /lib/libncurses.so.5.6 /lib/libncurses.so

Then:
  make

Mac OS X
--------

Run 
 
  ./mac_makefiles

Before:

  make
